ğŸ“ Tee Networks â€” Enquiries & Contact Form
ğŸ§© Overview

This project contains the Enquiries Page for Tee Networks, built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
The page allows users to submit their enquiries through a modern, validated form with smooth styling and responsive design.

ğŸŒ Page Description

The Enquiries Page lets users:

Enter their full name, email address, subject, and message.

Get real-time validation before submission.

See visual feedback for successful or invalid inputs.

Experience a clean, responsive design that adapts to all devices.

